

The modular approach requires/implies a message interface for 
relating to other modules or parts of the whole system

On the more lower levels, it relies on Glue for transmitting the messages.


> on the level of SOM semantics, for passing around

  - visualization / interaction
  - vectors
  - tables
  - meta-control data
  - results
  - queries

> for preparing data according to transformer technology

> for post-processing according to sprite technology



